data.description: Great bones to make your own in this charming home situated in a great location and neighborhood with a fully fenced in yard perfect for social get togethers and potential gardening space! The main floor has hardwood flooring through out, open living room and kitchen, and a bonus area off the kitchen for potential storage/pantry. Three bedrooms on the upper floor with the primary featuring walk in closet and private balcony for a perfect relaxing spot. Oversized carport for bonus storage space and/or RV parking in addition to the partially finished basement!
